## Build the project

You don't need to follow this guide unless you want to build the Python package on your own.

### Prerequisites
- Python
- cargo (install via [rust](https://rustup.rs/))
- [uv](https://github.com/astral-sh/uv) (python package manager)

### Build

```bash
uv sync
uv build
```


